data.description: Unlock the potential of this expansive 3-bedroom, 2 ½ bathroom single-family home nestled in the heart of Palm Desert. With its enduring charm, this property offers a canvas for creating a personalized modern desert retreat.    Step through the double door entry into the light-filled living room/great room, seamlessly connecting to the backyard, where the outdoor oasis awaits. The family room, also accessible to the backyard, features a comforting fireplace, making it an ideal space for relaxation.    The kitchen, equipped with stainless steel appliances and a convenient breakfast bar, is ready for your culinary inspirations and awaits your personal touch to bring it to life.    Embrace the allure of outdoor living in the private backyard oasis, boasting a captivating pool and spa tub, surrounded by mature landscaping and a patio covering. Take in the  sneak peek of the mountains while relishing the serenity of this perfect setting for relaxation and lively gatherings.    The primary ensuite bedroom offers a spacious and tastefully updated shower and tub area, while the dressing area invites a slight cosmetic update. With a dual vanity and ample storage space provided by two closets, this ensuite offers the opportunity to create a luxurious and rejuvenating sanctuary, with the added bonus of direct access to the backyard.     Situated on a corner lot within the development and tucked away in a prime location, this home offers easy access to the renowned shopping and dining experiences of El Paseo, as well as the excitement of the Indian Wells Tennis Gardens. Seize this incredible opportunity to transform this Palm Desert gem into your very own modern desert paradise.
